    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by its sole owner. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with absolutely no scratches, dings, or imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling new. Mechanically, the car performs flawlessly, having been garage-kept and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
