    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of peerless distinction, maintained in impeccable, showroom condition. This unit exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a standard of care that preserves its original factory integrity. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the pristine cabin, remains in a state of absolute refinement. Engineered for the most demanding enthusiasts, this vehicle represents a rare convergence of aesthetic perfection and mechanical excellence. We invite only the most discerning buyers to experience this investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 44900.0,
